<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA624_01_IH_0003</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema624_01.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_01_ih_0003">
      <section class="title flex_wrap">
        <h2 lang="y">
          <span class="recap" lang="y">이전에 <span>배웠어요</span></span>
          <span class="title_text" lang="y">『수학 6-1』 비와 비율 알아보기</span>
        </h2>
      </section>
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="3_deep_green" lang="y">은호는 투호살 10개를 던져서 병 속에 2개를 넣었습니다. 던진 투호살 수에 대한 넣은 투호살 수의 비율을 소수로 나타내어 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center">
          <div class="input_wrap">
            <math-field data-answer-single="0.2"></math-field>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
					<div class="inner_solve">
						<div class="flex">
							<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
							<div class="conts_solve">
								<p class="mixed_fraction">던진 투호살 수에 대한 넣은 투호살 수의 비율은
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>2</span>
                    <span>10</span>
                  </span>=0.2입니다.
                </p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
